{
  "text": "The first part of the discussion focuses on the positive aspects of the framework presented above. Such a framework may assist different users (learners, educators and the institution itself) to achieve their educational goals. The framework includes a new cohort of SWBES that are useful for enhancing and improving business processes and that improve the quality of service delivery with social software / semantic web technology [CITATION_1] .",
